comment._content: VP-16 P2V-5 (BuNo unknown) HH-7 at Forrest Sherman Field, NAS Pensacola, FL, 10 May 1957. Tail code changed to "LF' July 01, 1957. The LAST was: Patrol Squadron SEVENTY FOUR (VP-74)redesignated Medium Patrol Squadron (Seaplane)TEN (VP-MS-10) on 15 November 1946.
